{"tid":2315843,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)肚餓遊戲1-4","createTime":"2020-12-07T12:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T18:17:06.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2e057772e5f1aeb223f0db24914e0716beb84c2c","tid":2315843,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=989f2d05\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=0ea0609c\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=639b7b01\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/d/d7/The_Hunger_Games_Mockingjay_-_Part_2_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fd%2Fd7%2FThe_Hunger_Games_Mockingjay_-_Part_2_Poster.jpg&h=aa40a834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.故事內容背景為一個位於北美洲的一個反烏托邦的虛構國家「施惠國」，由史諾總統統治12個行政區。施惠國為了維持恐怖的統治制度以及鎮壓人民，他們有一個作為懲罰過去在第13區的起義及平息社會叛亂，以及用來瓦解地區的方法，每個行政區必須提供兩個「貢品」&mdash; 通過抽籤選定12至18歲的男孩和女孩各一人，投身於年度盛會，每年必須在電視直播的《飢餓遊戲》中競爭，他們必須在一個廣闊舞台上戰鬥至死，唯一倖存者在最後將會獲得名與利..<br />\n<br />\n2.在第74屆飢餓遊戲勝出後，凱妮絲與比德以勝利者的姿態回到第12區的家鄉，二人都獲得豐厚的獎金，從此衣食無憂，凱妮絲原以為生活自此便安定下來，回到家鄉的她卻患上創傷後壓力症。原來她在比賽的最後關頭，迫使國會改變比賽規則的舉措，讓民眾視為反抗國會暴政的代表人物，此舉除了讓國會面目無光外..<br />\n<br />\n3.故事承接上一集，敘述凱妮絲在遊戲中獲救後將與普魯塔克和黑密契對都城展開革命....。<br />\n「燃燒的女孩」凱妮絲艾佛丁在大旬祭上被反抗軍救走，比德卻不幸落入都城手裡。<br />\n凱妮絲被帶到傳說中已成廢墟的第13區，在反抗軍領袖柯茵和戰友支持下，銜命成為革命的象徵，領導施惠國各區叛變，對抗專制又腐敗的都城，同時也心繫比德安危，傾力籌劃營救行動..<br />\n<br />\n4.故事承接上集：迫於情勢，凱妮絲艾佛丁開始領導施惠國的各區叛變，對抗專制又腐敗的都城。隨著這場決定施惠國命運的戰爭愈演愈烈，都城控制下的其他區也趨向毀滅。凱妮絲必須確定她能信任誰及她需要完成的使命，以免她所愛的一切遭受危及..<br />\n<br />\n8 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=7d4e6009\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTtUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=cb771ab4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d83056fa3b0fa55abb0ea6adbccb29ed4f58945","tid":2315843,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T12:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse